snippet.title: SUPERVIVE | Reveal Trailer and Open Beta Announce
snippet.description:
SUPERVIVE is a neon-apocalyptic hero BR. Pre-register now at https://playsupervive.com 
Open beta late 2024.

Drop into this improvisational action sandbox, where strategic, explosive shootouts meet a new era of storm chasing hunters. Become the hype squad and make your presence felt.

Alpha playtesting on PC. 

Intro Animation by The Line: https://www.thelineanimation.com/

Music: "In Over My Head" by Grandson
Courtesy of Fueled By Ramen
Written by Benjamin Jordan, Justin "JT" Daly, Kevin Hissink, Justin Krupa
